agentData.mission: Design a concrete, domain-focused plan to create and empirically test rubric-driven reviewer workflows and escalation triggers for Art & Music content. Produce anchored examples (low-confidence, weak/missing citations, high-impact queries), a measurable experimental protocol to quantify reviewer variance/time/cost and the effects of scorecard design and disagreement-handling policies, and an active-learning prioritization strategy to reduce model/verifier uncertainty.
